美国国家飓风中心在米奇处于最高强度时指出，“暂时还不能确定加勒比地区西北部的哪个或哪些国家所受威胁最大。”到10月26日晚，美国海军运作全球大气预报系统预测，飓风会继续西进袭击[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]；[[地球物理流体动力学实验室|地球物理流体动力学实验室]]的计算机模型则预计风暴会在西加勒比海总体保持向北移动<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031060542/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.021 | date = 1998-10-26 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 21 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.021 | archivedate = 2008-10-31}}</ref>。米奇在最高强度下保持了约12小时，并在此期间行进至洪都拉斯近海的[[天鹅群岛|天鹅群岛]]上空。风暴略向西面转向，但气象机构仍然预计气旋会转向北上<ref name="tcr" />。10月27日，风眼周围的对流变得模糊<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | date = 1998-10-27 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031054359/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.024 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.024 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。由于南半部环流进入洪都拉斯上空，南面气流无法得到有效补充，米奇逐渐减弱<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | date = 1998-10-27 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 25 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.025 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031063637/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.025 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2008-10-31}}</ref>。风眼变得有些模糊<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 1998-10-28 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 26 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031070802/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.026 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.026}}</ref>，10月28日清晨，米奇的强度已低于五级飓风标准<ref name="tcr" />。

气象机构在当时的实际操作中没有发现墨西哥湾上空存在弱中层反气旋，受其影响，米奇于10月27日开始缓慢转向南下，从距[[瓜纳哈岛|瓜纳哈岛]]非常近的洋面掠过<ref name="tcr" />。美国国家飓风中心预计，风暴会在[[洪都拉斯湾|洪都拉斯湾]]以小规模环路移动，这一动向只是环状路径的组成部分，不过该机构也表示对这一预测不是很有把握<ref>{{cite report | author = John Guiney | date = 1998-10-28 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 27 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031073705/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.027 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.027}}</ref>。气旋有可能进入[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]周期，还受到陆地和[[上升流|上升流]]的不利影响<ref>{{cite report | author = Ed Rappaport | date = 1998-10-28 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.029 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031080459/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.029}}</ref>，导致结构继续瓦解，其强度于10月28日晚降至低于大型飓风标准<ref name="tcr" />。10月29日，米奇以风力时速130公里强度从[[拉塞瓦|拉塞瓦]][[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]洪都拉斯<ref name="tcr" />。虽然气旋已进入陆地上空，但美国国家飓风中心仍然预计飓风会转向北上并因此重新增强<ref>{{cite report | author = John Guiney | date = 1998-10-29 | title = Hurricane Mitch Discussion Number 31 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.031 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031073254/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.031}}</ref>。

10月29日晚，米奇降级成热带风暴。气旋缓慢穿越洪都拉斯，逐渐转向西进。风暴的大规模环流令[[中美洲|中美洲]]普降暴雨，引发大范围洪灾，其中又以洪都拉斯和[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]情况严重。<ref name="tcr" />米奇在陆上行进期间起初还能保有深层对流区<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | date = 1998-10-30 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 36 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031082310/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.036 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.036}}</ref>，风速也一直保持在热带风暴标准<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | date = 1998-10-30 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 37 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031084750/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.037 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.037 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2008-10-31}}</ref>。10月31日，由于气旋行经陆地逐渐转为山区，环流结构因此变得混乱，不过最强的对流一直在附近的太平洋水域持续存在，美国国家飓风中心指出，米奇有可能成为[[太平洋飓风季|太平洋热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | date = 1998-10-31 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 39 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031082843/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.039 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.039}}</ref>。当晚，风暴在[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]和洪都拉斯边境附近降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。墨西哥湾西部上空的高压脊因受逐渐逼近的低压槽影响而弱化，米奇终于得以转向西北<ref>{{cite report | author = John Guiney | date = 1998-10-31 | title = Tropical Depression Mitch Discussion Number 41 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.041 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031062840/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.041 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2008-10-31}}</ref>。对流逐渐消亡<ref>{{cite report | author = Ed Rappaport | date = 1998-11-01 | title = Tropical Depression Mitch Discussion Number 42 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.042 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031073132/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.042}}</ref>，11月1日，行进至墨西哥和危地马拉边境的米奇已经失去下层环流<ref name="tcr" />。

== 再生并转变成温带气旋 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Mitch.JPG|left]]上空的热带风暴米奇，组织结构较为混乱。]]

虽然下层低气压中心已经消散，但米奇的残留仍然保有高空环流，于11月2日进入[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]，并在当天开始再度发展出对流<ref name="tcr" />。11月3日晚，飓风猎人发现系统中有层次分明的下层中心，飞行高度层风速每小时95公里。美国国家飓风中心为此开始再度针对尤卡坦半岛[[坎佩切|坎佩切]]西南偏西方向约90公里洋面的米奇发布公告<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 1998-11-03 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 46 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.046 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031055547/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.046 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。再生期间，米奇因受逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响向东北偏东方向移动<ref name="disc47">{{cite report | author = Ed Rappaport | date = 1998-11-04 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 47 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.047 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031074702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.047 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。11月4日清晨，气旋以风力时速65公里强度从坎佩切以北不远处登陆，并在穿越尤卡坦半岛期间快速弱化成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。

米奇位于墨西哥东部上空期间，其深层对流组成的雨带位于东部边缘。美国国家飓风中心预计，附近洋面水温较高，还有可能受[[斜压|斜压]]影响，所以气旋有望再度强化<ref name="disc47" />。11月4日，米奇第二次进入墨西哥湾并再次增强成热带风暴<ref name="tcr" />，不过系统核心附近的对流很少，最强风力距中心尚有超过370公里，表明米奇这时已不完全是热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | author = Ed Rappaport | date = 1998-11-04 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 49 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031074951/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.049 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.049}}</ref>。系统加速向佛罗里达州海岸前进，并在此期间与逼近的冷锋相互影响<ref name="tcr" />。11月5日，环流变得拉长，美国国家飓风中心称，如果不是因为这片天气系统属于米奇的残留，那么可能不会将之视为热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | author = Max Mayfield | date = 1998-11-05 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 51 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.051 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031085103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.051 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风暴增强至每小时100公里风速，然后从[[那不勒斯_(佛罗里达州)|那不勒斯]]附近登陆佛罗里达州西南部。气旋迅速穿越该州，产生5场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]和热带风暴强度大风，然后进入大西洋西南部<ref name="tcr" />。11月5日晚，飓风猎人侦察机无法在米奇内部找到明显的中心，而是发现有拉长的环流嵌入冷锋之中。美国国家飓风中心据此宣布米奇已转变成温带气旋。<ref>{{cite report | author = Ed Rappaport | date = 1998-11-05 | title = Tropical Storm Mitch Discussion Number 54 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2008-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.054 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031081442/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1398.054}}</ref>

米奇的温带残留继续快速向东北方向移动，于11月6日从[[百慕大|百慕大]]以北经过，其风速在次日略有增强，达到每小时110公里。到了11月9日，系统残留已从[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]以西掠过，美国国家飓风中心于当晚停止对其加以监控。<ref name="tcr" />

